                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559339352-11d035aa65de?w=600&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Good Cup Coffee">
                <span class="card-badge">☕ SPECIALTY</span>
                <span class="card-vibe"><i class="fas fa-coffee"></i> Chill</span>
            </div>
            <div class="card-content">
                <h3>Good Cup Coffee</h3>
                <p class="card-location"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> AS Fortuna, Mandaue City</p>
                <div class="rating">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                    <span>4.8 (234 reviews)</span>
                </div>
                <p>Single-origin brews, minimalist industrial vibe, award-winning pastries.</p>
                <div class="card-actions">
                    <button class="btn-crave" onclick="addToCravings('Good Cup Coffee', 1, 'restaurant')">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i> Crave
                    </button>
